00:20:07.140 --> 00:20:10.839
tools, Lightning Talks, you know, Brown Bag Lunches and all this.

00:20:10.839 --> 00:20:18.199
One day I just rented, I just reserved a conference room and I said, hey, you know, I'm inviting

00:20:18.199 --> 00:20:20.699
everyone to just come in and let's just code together.

00:20:20.699 --> 00:20:23.000
You don't have to talk, you don't have to do any of that.

00:20:23.000 --> 00:20:25.160
Let's just sit and code.

00:20:25.160 --> 00:20:30.520
And it turned out that like three or four projects came out of the first one.

00:20:30.520 --> 00:20:35.280
Because people, one, I remember one instance, it was somebody needed help debugging and

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:40.599
