I've tried to either evangelize R or Python to.

00:26:38.640 --> 00:26:43.560
I find that neither language has a great, you know, acceptance rate for someone who's

00:26:43.560 --> 00:26:46.760
been very invested in the other, in SAS.

00:26:47.920 --> 00:26:53.359
My experience with R and Python and which one to choose, if you're working closer to a

00:26:53.359 --> 00:26:59.040
