could actually do this in like one line, like t.tests replaces, you know, whatever

00:28:36.520 --> 00:28:38.959
else I would have done in SAS, you know?

00:28:39.599 --> 00:28:44.000
So I find it's easier to transition people from SAS to R.

00:28:44.000 --> 00:28:48.119
Like I said, it's not general for every single person, but for the most people,

00:28:49.560 --> 00:28:50.839
trust me, R is the way to go.

